 least-expensive file sharing sites available. Each plan Transfer BigFiles offers is ideal for a specific size of business. A standout feature of this file sharing site is that it doesn’t apply bandwidth limitations to any plan, which makes the file uploading and sharing processes much faster and smoother.","Transfer BigFiles places a 2GB limit on the files you can share. However, this file sharing service does not place any type of restriction on the type of file you can send. You can send Word documents, images, music files, PowerPoint presentations and more.","If you plan to share large files on a frequent basis, the desktop application this service offers (which is compatible with both Windows and Mac systems) is a feature you’ll love. This drag-and-drop application lets you add files quickly and easily, and it even lets you send multiple transfers simultaneously, bypassing the 2GB web upload limit. The app also lets you upload entire folders and resume uploads in cases when your network connection is lost. A mobile app is also provided.","There are dropbox capabilities available that allow you to add a widget to your website where clients and colleagues can directly upload files to send them to you. However, we are disappointed that there is no MS Outlook plugin that would allow you to integrate this file sharing service with your Outlook account. This functionality would make sharing files much easier and would save you the time you&#39;ll spend searching and importing your contacts&#39; information.","Transfer BigFiles provides several tracking tools that allow you to monitor your most important files. Recipient download notifications are sent to your inbox when a recipient downloads a file. You can also view your account history in the History tab when you&#39;re logged in to your account. Here you can view everything from the date the file was uploaded to how many times it’s been downloaded.","Transfer BigFiles offers all the critical security features necessary for sending large files online. The company provides SSL secure and encrypted transfers, as well as password-protected downloads to ensure that only approved individuals can download your files.","The customer support available from this file sharing site is meager. You&#39;ll find support for Transfer BigFiles by going to the Support link at the top of the site&#39;s homepage. In this area, you’ll find FAQs that provide answers to a handful of questions. There is no knowledgebase available, and an email support is the only form of direct communication with a representative that we were able to find."]},"id":"a2c745f8-79d8-4f03-a242-6945445b2159","type":"text"},{"data":{"text":"Summary"},"id":"2f6b107c-0ed3-4f75-81b6-13ac54cf3f57","type":"heading"},{"data":{"paragraphs":["Transfer BigFiles is a well-rounded file sharing service that provides a range of plans and has powerful features and attractive applications. This service offers generous features such as unlimited bandwidth, unlimited sends and customized dropboxes. However, we are disappointed in the lack of MS Outlook integration and with the limited customer service options. Overall, Transfer BigFiles is an online file sharing site that is more basic than other services but still provides excellent results."]},"id":"f1efb767-26ee-4c78-bbc4-2b515387ffb1","type":"text"}]],"body":null,"legacyId":"product_review_page_53540","url":"/transferbigfiles-com-review","authors":[{"email":"","slug":"jeph-preece","url":"/author/jeph-preece","dateCreated":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","name":"Jeph Preece","dateModified":"2019-04-17T20:46:58Z","id":"UEqrRM5xmXnCHCjkbS6o5e","dateImported":null,"site":"toptenreviews"}],"territories":["US","GB"],"companies":[],"dateCreated":"2011-08-31T16:51:30Z","datePublished":"2011-08-31T16:51:30Z","name":"Transfer BigFiles","synopsis":"Editor’s Note: This service has been removed from viewing as part of this site because it has been replaced by another product. You can still read our original